title: FSX/FS9 Commercial Level Simulations Piper Arrow
description:
From the website:
Want something smaller then Airbus or Boeing? We got the perfect small prop for you! This Piper Arrow will give you hours of fun.

 

Features:

-          Highly detailed 3D models

-          3D Virtual Cockpit

-     All standard animations

-          Opening door

-          8 liveries for free

-          Dynamic shine

-          Fully animated control surfaces

-          FDE based on real world pilot input

-          4 different panel styles for black, blue, brown and silver/grey

-          Matching VC to panel color

-          Paint kit

-          Operation manual and panel description
